{"tid":2119902,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】藍店稻香潮庭違限罩限桌令無被控 醫生斥不公：倘黃店已受極刑","createTime":"2020-07-22T11:01:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T11:53:10.000Z","uid":48083,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7cfc660922b49f6e860356a18301062b98f4ca86","tid":2119902,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T11:01:26.000Z","msg":"第三波武漢肺炎疫情衍生出稻香、潮庭、富臨3大「藍店」感染群組，而且3間酒樓均涉嫌違反社交限制措施。但食環署只對最遲爆疫的富臨提出檢控，影片證明數百食客「除罩」跳舞唱歌的稻香、衞生防護中心表明一枱坐十多位賓客連患者的潮庭，食環署仍未提控甚至調查。本身是醫生的立法會議員郭家麒狠批港府執法不公、刻意放生「藍店」至最後一刻，「調轉係『黃店』，一早被處以極刑喇！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200722/TULYT6S32FL7WXTWZ5HET3ONXY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200722%2FTULYT6S32FL7WXTWZ5HET3ONXY%2F&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtBx3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=2883f528\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200722%2FTULYT6S32FL7WXTWZ5HET3ONXY%2F&h=25f7c7f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200722/TULYT6S32FL7WXTWZ5HET3ONXY/</a>"},{"pid":"f7bd09bd82e4e3ed8370416e8608533240369cf2","tid":2119902,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T11:17:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"296e40157d1b2641c8fcced6d73049cf07ef384e","tid":2119902,"uid":331551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T11:18:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8c7e1aeab740fa2451547988abd83c20a356246c","tid":2119902,"uid":230609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T11:30:08.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"5a08074dd4fb6de182d7fb89c1db99b0b4b7ffc1","tid":2119902,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T11:32:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7225b9ea52a83afba15e63c219d586a7145c808c","tid":2119902,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T11:33:47.000Z","msg":"法西斯係咁..."},{"pid":"f13ace7918c33ebb67e84265ab9c3736b99f31a8",